 # 🌐 Web UI Prototype (React & Tailwind)

This folder contains the frontend source code and design assets for the **AI Toll Tax Management System v3.0**. 

We developed this interactive web application to visually demonstrate the operational value of our C++ backend logic to non-technical stakeholders. It simulates the entire stop-free automation pipeline in a modern, user-friendly interface.

### 🚀 [CLICK HERE TO VIEW THE LIVE INTERACTIVE PROTOTYPE]
### 🌐 [CLICK HERE TO VIEW OUR LIVE INTERACTIVE WEB PROTOTYPE](https://toll-tax.lovable.app)

## 📊 Prototype Features
* **AI Toll Gate Simulator:** A visual pipeline demonstrating the ALPR camera verification, National Database cross-checking, and AI Weight Fraud detection in real-time.
* **Live Dashboard:** Dynamic updates of Total Revenue, Vehicles Processed, and Security Flags as simulated vehicles pass through the gate.
* **FASTag Wallet Management:** Simulated auto-billing, digital balance tracking, and low-balance warnings.
* **Audit & Security Logs:** Immutable tracking of exempt vehicles (Ambulances), weight mismatches, and flagged stolen vehicles.

